title: Husband of ex-US Senate candidate Annette Bosworth indicted
text: SIOUX FALLS, S.D. (AP) - The husband of former U.S. Senate candidate Annette Bosworth has been indicted on election law violations in connection with his wife's problematic 2014 campaign. A Hughes County indictment charges Chad Haber with one count each of offering false or forged instrument for filing and perjury. ... ...
